criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of pelvic gynecological cancer posed on initial histological analysis or
             during recurrence;

          -  Or diagnosis of endometriosis on histology or imaging

          -  Age ≥ 18 years;

          -  Affiliation to the general social security scheme;

          -  Consent signed.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Refusal of the patient;

          -  Non-affiliation to the general social security scheme.
